FORM GET_EXCEPTION_DIFFERENCE
 TABLES DIFFERENCES STRUCTURE UNTERSCHIED.
 IF VEXCEPTION NE OEXCEPTION.
   MOVE 'EXCEPTION' TO DIFFERENCES-PARAMETER.
   IF VEXCEPTION = SPACE.
     MOVE '-' TO DIFFERENCES-ALT.
   ELSE.
     MOVE VEXCEPTION TO DIFFERENCES-ALT.
   ENDIF.
   IF OEXCEPTION = SPACE.
     MOVE '-' TO DIFFERENCES-NEU.
   ELSE.
     MOVE OEXCEPTION TO DIFFERENCES-NEU.
   ENDIF.
   APPEND DIFFERENCES.
  ENDIF.
ENDFORM.
FORM COMPARE_DATA
                  TABLES DIFFERENCES STRUCTURE UNTERSCHIED
                  USING FIELD
                  CHANGING RETCODE.
 DATA : SUBRC LIKE SY-SUBRC.
 field-symbols: <l_f1> type x.
 field-symbols: <l_f2> type x.
 RETCODE = '='.
 CLEAR DIFFERENCES.
 CASE FIELD.
 WHEN 'O_VALUE'.
IF %_OO_VALUE
NE %_VO_VALUE.
RETCODE = SPACE.
MOVE FIELD TO DIFFERENCES-PARAMETER.
assign %_VO_VALUE to <l_f1> casting.
assign differences-alt to <l_f2> casting.
<l_f2> = <l_f1>.
assign %_OO_VALUE to <l_f1> casting.
assign differences-neu to <l_f2> casting.
<l_f2> = <l_f1>.
APPEND DIFFERENCES.
ENDIF.
 WHEN 'C_VALUE'.
IF %_OC_VALUE
NE %_VC_VALUE.
RETCODE = SPACE.
MOVE FIELD TO DIFFERENCES-PARAMETER.
assign %_VC_VALUE to <l_f1> casting.
assign differences-alt to <l_f2> casting.
<l_f2> = <l_f1>.
assign %_OC_VALUE to <l_f1> casting.
assign differences-neu to <l_f2> casting.
<l_f2> = <l_f1>.
APPEND DIFFERENCES.
ENDIF.
 WHEN 'N_VALUE'.
IF %_ON_VALUE
NE %_VN_VALUE.
RETCODE = SPACE.
MOVE FIELD TO DIFFERENCES-PARAMETER.
assign %_VN_VALUE to <l_f1> casting.
assign differences-alt to <l_f2> casting.
<l_f2> = <l_f1>.
assign %_ON_VALUE to <l_f1> casting.
assign differences-neu to <l_f2> casting.
<l_f2> = <l_f1>.
APPEND DIFFERENCES.
ENDIF.
 WHEN 'P_VALUE'.
IF %_OP_VALUE
NE %_VP_VALUE.
RETCODE = SPACE.
MOVE FIELD TO DIFFERENCES-PARAMETER.
assign %_VP_VALUE to <l_f1> casting.
assign differences-alt to <l_f2> casting.
<l_f2> = <l_f1>.
assign %_OP_VALUE to <l_f1> casting.
assign differences-neu to <l_f2> casting.
<l_f2> = <l_f1>.
APPEND DIFFERENCES.
ENDIF.
WHEN 'I_TAB'.
DO.
READ TABLE %_OI_TAB INDEX SY-INDEX.
SUBRC = SY-SUBRC.
READ TABLE %_VI_TAB INDEX SY-INDEX.
IF SY-SUBRC NE 0 AND SUBRC NE 0.
EXIT.
ELSEIF SY-SUBRC NE 0.
RETCODE = SPACE.
MOVE FIELD TO DIFFERENCES-PARAMETER.
assign %_OI_TAB to <l_f1> casting.
assign differences-neu to <l_f2> casting.
<l_f2> = <l_f1>.
APPEND DIFFERENCES.
EXIT.
ELSEIF SUBRC NE 0.
RETCODE = SPACE.
MOVE FIELD TO DIFFERENCES-PARAMETER.
assign %_VI_TAB to <l_f1> casting.
assign differences-alt to <l_f2> casting.
<l_f2> = <l_f1>.
APPEND DIFFERENCES.
EXIT.
ELSEIF %_VI_TAB
NE %_OI_TAB.
RETCODE = SPACE.
MOVE FIELD TO DIFFERENCES-PARAMETER.
assign %_VI_TAB to <l_f1> casting.
assign differences-alt to <l_f2> casting.
<l_f2> = <l_f1>.
assign %_OI_TAB to <l_f1> casting.
assign differences-neu to <l_f2> casting.
<l_f2> = <l_f1>.
APPEND DIFFERENCES.
EXIT.
ENDIF.
ENDDO.
WHEN 'EXCEPTION'.
IF VEXCEPTION NE OEXCEPTION.
RETCODE = SPACE.
MOVE FIELD      TO DIFFERENCES-PARAMETER.
MOVE VEXCEPTION TO DIFFERENCES-ALT.
MOVE OEXCEPTION TO DIFFERENCES-NEU.
APPEND DIFFERENCES.
ENDIF.
  ENDCASE.
ENDFORM.